OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChurch says abuse          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcompensation scheme        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'broadest yet'             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Church of England has announced    
OL,6, plans for what it says is the broadest 
OL,7, and most ambitious compensation scheme 
OL,8, of its kind for victims of abuse.      
OL,10,FBut survivors waiting years for redress
OL,11,Fsay they had hoped for more details on 
OL,12,Fwhen the scheme will be rolled out.    
OL,14,FIt will be open to anyone who has faced
OL,15,Fphysical, sexual, emotional or         
OL,16,Fspiritual abuse by someone representing
OL,17,Fthe Church.                            
OL,19,FBut some fear being re-traumatised by  
OL,20,Fthe application process.               
